      "lineNumber": 11,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "DISABLED \u2014 httpbin.org returned 503 (rate-limited from repeated test runs).\nRe-enable the steps below when the http suite is revisited.\n- save \u0027test upload content\u0027 to \u0027upload-test.txt\u0027\n- upload upload-test.txt to https://httpbin.org/post, unsigned, write to %response%\n- if %response% is not empty then\n- write out \u0027Upload returned response\u0027\n- if %response.StatusCode% equals 200 then\n- write out \u0027Status code is 200\u0027\n- delete file \u0027upload-test.txt\u0027",
